{"tid":2281694,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"王嘉爾被爆戀愛「牽網紅上夜店」　真相影片公開傻眼了！","createTime":"2020-11-11T10:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T17:52:28.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":246,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b7117b69125782dc0680f0a9a172458faa516121","tid":2281694,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"藝人王嘉爾是韓團GOT7的成員之一，靠著帥氣的外表與反差萌的逗趣個性，吸引了大批少女追捧，也獲邀到大陸錄製多部綜藝，很有商業頭腦的他在年中開設自創時裝品牌「TEAM WANG」，怎料事業有成的他11日竟被大陸網友爆料牽手網紅上夜店還登上了微博熱搜，引起大批網友討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/d5263370.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2Fd5263370.jpg&h=47ee75f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾11日爆出戀愛說。（圖／翻攝自王嘉爾微博）<br />\n<br />\n王嘉爾11日突然登上了微博熱搜，原來是有大陸網友貼出一系列動圖，指稱他牽手知名網紅Iris上夜店玩樂，只見他穿著自家品牌「TEAM WANG」的上衣，在燈光昏暗的舞池裡，將穿著白色露肩上衣的Iris一把牽到旁邊，親密的舉動讓戀愛說立刻在網路上發酵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/d5263366.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2Fd5263366.jpg&h=96fa6832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/d5263365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2Fd5263365.jpg&h=18756fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾7月開設自創品牌。（圖／翻攝自王嘉爾微博）<br />\n<br />\n只不過，王嘉爾戀愛說瘋傳後，粉絲立刻跳出來放出牽手動圖的完整影片，其實當晚是他自創品牌的after party，開幕當天邀請了許多知名網紅到場站台，而從完整影片看來他似乎是為了招呼女方，先是伸手跟遠方的朋友示意，加上場地太擁擠的關係，出於貼心才將女方牽到一旁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/5263371.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2F5263371.gif&h=6387129c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/d5263367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2Fd5263367.jpg&h=5a5068ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾被爆牽手網紅Iris上夜店。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n對此，王嘉爾粉絲面對偶像再度被抹黑，也忍不住直呼「當天根本就是公開活動，沒有什麼牽手、戀愛一事」、「這一次的造謠也太假了吧」，另外也有不少網友看了影片後狂讚「只覺得王嘉爾好紳士」、「看得出是非常有親和力的藝人阿」意外引起許多熱議。<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到缺點既男人"},{"pid":"b146caa25beeb0c23e6649cf29b7f75b00e9f5fb","tid":2281694,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:28:30.000Z","msg":"條女幾似禮志"},{"pid":"527fdaa5f97f4bbd68045e33d69da6f6133a9f65","tid":2281694,"uid":240447,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:30:46.000Z","msg":"樓主係jacky<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"605e504d9cb05630b2646de1255e300b5280a969","tid":2281694,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"527fdaa5f97f4bbd68045e33d69da6f6133a9f65","tid":2281694,"uid":240447,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:30:46.000Z","msg":"樓主係jacky<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:31:15.000Z","msg":"層主都係"},{"pid":"fe0de5de3de31caae0957dab46e65565cc391242","tid":2281694,"uid":153600,"like":116,"dislike":3,"score":113,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:33:43.000Z","msg":"一個背叛我哋香港人嘅偽人仲有乜嘢好關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cb6f10878078b0980e201ff79d304f536efa437","tid":2281694,"uid":374400,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"唔想見到佢個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次唔po佢嘅相得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eeac2eb3729561c50fcc29a63b48f6183410fcc","tid":2281694,"uid":74065,"like":255,"dislike":4,"score":251,"quote":{"pid":"fe0de5de3de31caae0957dab46e65565cc391242","tid":2281694,"uid":153600,"like":116,"dislike":3,"score":113,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:33:43.000Z","msg":"一個背叛我哋香港人嘅偽人仲有乜嘢好關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy"