mages/5263/d5263365.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2Fd5263365.jpg&h=18756fd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾7月開設自創品牌。（圖／翻攝自王嘉爾微博）<br />\n<br />\n只不過，王嘉爾戀愛說瘋傳後，粉絲立刻跳出來放出牽手動圖的完整影片，其實當晚是他自創品牌的after party，開幕當天邀請了許多知名網紅到場站台，而從完整影片看來他似乎是為了招呼女方，先是伸手跟遠方的朋友示意，加上場地太擁擠的關係，出於貼心才將女方牽到一旁。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/5263371.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2F5263371.gif&h=6387129c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5263/d5263367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5263%2Fd5263367.jpg&h=5a5068ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲王嘉爾被爆牽手網紅Iris上夜店。（圖／翻攝自微博）<br />\n<br />\n對此，王嘉爾粉絲面對偶像再度被抹黑，也忍不住直呼「當天根本就是公開活動，沒有什麼牽手、戀愛一事」、「這一次的造謠也太假了吧」，另外也有不少網友看了影片後狂讚「只覺得王嘉爾好紳士」、「看得出是非常有親和力的藝人阿」意外引起許多熱議。<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到缺點既男人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:48:08.000Z","msg":"太矮"},{"pid":"4172fb22e1d08cf5c3615130198c19b3491b1858","tid":2281694,"uid":176586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:50:29.000Z","msg":"who？"},{"pid":"7eedfe26316bab251473ec154da37a2d642820d9","tid":2281694,"uid":15371,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:01:39.000Z","msg":"王嘉爾oppa日日草粉<br />\n呢個網紅都只係其中一個<br />\n無乜必要驚訝"},{"pid":"2c4c1ab08f321326d0be2687ca021e7ef1653078","tid":2281694,"uid":128741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"addebb09914f1fab0fb991617f8e09cc7dcd46c5","tid":2281694,"uid":238475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc500c94b6db2a6adbd7d5fc59d1297cec569174","tid":2281694,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"17eadd02f9d6f663e9560909929f6a3d48aa75d7","tid":2281694,"uid":238475,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，什麼叫傻眼?"},"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T10:39:43.000Z","msg":"指因某人事物過於出乎意料而驚訝地說